  "texts": [
    "In other words, it is estimated that roughly 60,000 scientific articles have been implicated in the use of LLM's (Gray 2024; Stokel-Walker 2024).",
    "Pointing to the rise of specific key words and phrases that occur more frequently with AI-generated text than in human writing (Gray 2024; Stokel-Walker 2024).",
    "A non-exhaustive list includes keywords such as commendable, meticulous, delve and the phrase complex and multifaceted (Gray 2024; Stokel-Walker 2024).",
    "Another study in the field of computer science estimated that 17.5 percent of scientific papers displayed characteristics indicative of AI and LLM utilization (Liang et al. 2024a, b; Stokel-Walker 2024).",
    "The \"certainly, here is a possible introduction for your topic\" example adduced in the introduction is yet another example making headlines across various social media platforms (Stokel-Walker 2024)."
